articles.description: K.J. Maura scored a career-high 25 points with a career-tying six 3-pointers, Joe Sherburne added 13 points and three 3s and Maryland, Baltimore County beat Hartford 62-53 on Tuesday night in a battle for the No. 2 seed in the America East Tournament.
articles.headline: Maura scores career-high 25, UMBC beats Hartford 62-53

articles.description: Jontay Porter scored a career-high 24 points, including four 3-pointers, and Missouri ended its three-game losing streak with a 74-66 win at Vanderbilt on Tuesday night.
articles.headline: Porter scores 24, Missouri ends skid with win at Vanderbilt

articles.description: The Vols shoot 56 percent from the floor and outrebound the Bulldogs 34-24 to secure the win.
